A few errors in the above quotes.  First, in game he and his guild are accountable to the other guilds that they share content with (i.e. RTA Reps).  Secondly, on this forum he is still accountable to SOE.  SOE has banned played for posts to outside message boards, they have also &quot;fired&quot; Guides for such posts.  <br>
